info.description:
libzt (ZeroTier)

Peer-to-peer and cross-platform encrypted connections built right into your app or service. No drivers, no root, and no host configuration.
Examples, tutorials and API docs for Python and other languages: [github.com/zerotier/libzt](https://www.github.com/zerotier/libzt) *NOTE: The implementation of this language binding attempts to be as Pythonic as possible. If something is not as it should be, please make a pull request or issue. Thanks.*
info.keywords: zerotier p2p peer-to-peer sdwan sdn virtual network socket tcp udp zt encryption encrypted
